  "title": "Senior Staff Nurse - Up to $5k - Pasir Panjang (0580)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Location: Pasir Panjang</li>\n  <li>Working days : 5.5days</li>\n  <li>Monday 8am-4pm or 9am to 5pm</li>\n  <li>Sat / Sunday 9am-1pm</li>\n  <li>$4300 - $5000</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform patient assessment.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate patient care and provide quality nursing care for an assigned group of patients.</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate competency in clinical nursing skills and knowledge</li>\n  <li>Provide patient education for family members.</li>\n  <li>Record and maintain proper accurate documentation of patient's progress.</li>\n  <li>Assists doctors and attend to emergency calls whenever necessary.</li>\n  <li>Perform appropriate interventions for effective patient's outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Manage and monitor medical supplies, equipment and consumables inventory</li>\n  <li>Practise safety and infection control precautionary measures</li>\n  <li>Participate in patients' rehabilitation, involving the patients' family.</li>\n  <li>Manage rendered in the notes, medication records and charts of patients.</li>\n  <li>Participate in medical emergencies or crisis situations as appropriate.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in nursing , SNB registered</li>\n  <li>With relevant years of experience in nursing home, Geriatric or Palliative Care Setting</li>\n  <li>Senior Staff Nurse with experience in leading a team</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p>\n<p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
